                <![CDATA[Do you know the opportunity your Parts Department represents?]]>
</bodyBullet>
              <bodyBullet id="bb1" order="11">
                <![CDATA[<li>Auto parts are a $244 billion market</li>]]>
</bodyBullet>
              <bodyBullet id="bb2" order="12">
                <![CDATA[<li>Automotive accessories are a $38 billion market</li>]]>
</bodyBullet>
              <bodyBullet id="bb3" order="13">
                <![CDATA[<li>The average car buyer spends $400 on accessories within the first six months after purchase</li>]]>
</bodyBullet>
              <bodyBullet id="bb4" order="14">
